text:
Ah, there you are...
It's Mei Izumi-chan, right?

Oh...!
The old lady from the souvenir shop.
Did you come to see me?

I just wanted to cheer you on...
Are you working around here again tomorrow?

I see...
Well, do your best over there too.

I wonder if you'll be on TV...
If you are, I'll definitely cheer for you.

Thank you.
It makes me happy to hear you say that.

Haha,
you got a wonderful souvenir at the end there.
